        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK973">
<l>mēliruntu mēlallār mēlallar kīḻiruntuṅ </l>
<l>kīḻallār kīḻalla var</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though (raised) above, the base cannot become great; though (brought) low, the great cannot become base.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
